    "description": "A flaw in Ghost's 2FA mechanism allowed staff users to skip email-based 2FA. The issue affected Ghost v5.105.0 through v5.130.5 and Ghost v6.0.0 through v6.10.3, and was fixed in v5.130.6 and v6.11.0.",
